ŘPhilomena Mary Gilbert
1939 -2020
Originally from Limerick, Ireland,
Philomena moved to England,
Shortbutts Lane and then Upper ST John Street
and enjoyed a long career in the NHS,
working locally.
Forever in our hearts"„
